    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 widebody silhouette, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is beyond reproach; the critical IMS bearing and Rear Main Seal have been proactively addressed with LN Engineering components. The driving dynamics are anchored by the viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system and factory M030 sport suspension, providing surgical turn-in and massive lateral grip. Finished in concours-grade paint with a flawless cabin, this C4S exhibits zero bore scoring and pulls linearly to its 7,300 RPM redline. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
