      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features original, mirror-finish paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, showing zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather seats remain supple and matte with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by thick floor mats since day one. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and includes a complete set of keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive service history. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle, offering a pristine experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
